{"tid":1680424,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會之 [10.28民間研究]","createTime":"2019-10-28T22:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:50:08.000Z","uid":287999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"697991c717a01567e3ba25a6073cf43fefbf55bf","tid":1680424,"uid":287999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:24:27.000Z","msg":"民記希望收集香港抗爭者精神壓力既數據，寫成報告係國際社會要求人道救援，希望大家幫手填之餘仲幫手廣傳推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知份問卷好好好長，但係因為用左Standardized tools所以冇法，希望大家忍耐下幫幫手填左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問卷link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=9b120e3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n<br />\n由六月至今，香港人經歷了大大小小一連串密集的社會運動，我們希望以今次問卷研究，了解抗爭者至今的心理健康、社交狀況，以及對整個運動的意見，為反送中運動作出系統性、科學化的數據收集及建議。是次問卷調查直至10月29日晚上8時59分截止，希望大家支持。<br />\n<br />\nWe would once again like to conduct a survey on 28th October, for the purpose of collecting empirical data on the mental health status, social functioning, as well as the public opinion on the Movement for quantitative analysis.<br />\n<br />\nThe deadline for submission is 8:59pm on Tuesday 29th October 2019."},{"pid":"d8a73605d1cbea30a1513a6ffa8d4537aae1bfa6","tid":1680424,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:28:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9412c88bb986d53c00b7e1724dfc983c60e8c72","tid":1680424,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T22:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81a96da9c